snippet: The Ukrainian qualifier Lesia Tsurenko, ranked 54th, upset No. 9 Garbiñe Muguruza, 7-5, 6-1, in the Rogers Cup in Toronto.
abstract: Qualifier Lesia Tsurenko of Ukraine upsets 9th-ranked Gardine Muguruza in women's second round at Rogers Cup tennis tournament in Canada; other tournament results noted.
lead_paragraph: The Ukrainian qualifier Lesia Tsurenko, ranked 54th, upset No. 9 Garbiñe Muguruza, 7-5, 6-1, in the Rogers Cup in Toronto.
